name: Quaker City National Bank, Appellant, v. Brooks et al.
name_abbreviation: Quaker City National Bank v. Brooks

judges: Before Moschzisker, C. J., Frazer, Walling, Simpson, Kephart, Sadler and Schaffer, JJ.
parties: Quaker City National Bank, Appellant, v. Brooks et al.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
This is an appeal by plaintiff from an order discharging a rule for judgment against the garnishee on its answers to interrogatories. Such an order is interlocutory and not appealable: Brendlinger v. Riegel, 37 Pa. Superior Ct. 474.
The appeal is quashed.
